{
  "stem": "21788.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say there were 400 of us by that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Down in the-- they were on the ice mats, like pens.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my father, my sister, and my mother, and I, we went upstairs to, well, on deck, actually, and stayed on deck all night long and slept in a chair.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if we were allowed to or not, but that's where we were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And apparently, nobody, nobody chased us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got to the Shanghai Harbor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were met at the Shanghai Harbor by the Jewish committee who, again, herded us onto trucks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, my father being a dentist and being upper-middle class, we were not used to be treated like cattle, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that's the way it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the humanity, the density of the population-- we were used to a certain amount of space.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Chinese don't know that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were herded-- well, we were transported to Hongkou-- Hongkou was the district that most of the Jewish refugees lived in-- by the committee.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if you had any relatives over there who made arrangements for you to stay someplace, you were packed into the [NON-ENGLISH], into the homes, which were converted schools where quite a number of the refugees stayed between eight and 10 years.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some of the refugees already came in 1936, 1937.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Those were large halls where a hundred people at a time slept in bunks two-high, with the only privacy that they had between families of a sheet.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "These were the people who were unable to make any kind of a living in Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had a place for us to stay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And like I mentioned before, that particular place was on the ground floor.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
